txt.en: Your mission is to steal weapons from within a nearby Ekhamâti camp and defeat as many soldiers as you can. You must make it out before reinforcements arrive.

'[placeholder], there is an Ekhamâti camp in Khûd Zagin where their soldiers appear to be stockpiling weapons.\n\n'We are in need of your help to steal as many of their weapon caches as possible to hinder their attacks. I ask that you defeat any soldiers you run into during your time there as well.'
Your mission is to steal weapons from within a nearby Ekhamâti camp and defeat as many soldiers as you can. You must make it out before reinforcements arrive.
'You have done well to take the weapons from the hands of the Ekhamâti. We will put these to good use.'
There is no twist in this mission.
